comment_text: Sorry about the large paragraph, I just wanted to thank you so much, Alan. You have a special place in my heart, as your songs made my childhood, and I assume they had the same effect on others. Although this is a meme now, I clearly remember hearing this in many YouTube videos when I was little including the iconic "Minecraft mobs in real life" on my mom's phone. This song holds so many memories and I can't help but feel a wave of bittersweet nostalgia whenever hearing this song. It's awesome seeing where you came during all those years I grew up. Again, thank you so much Alan. Keep doing your awesome work, everyone loves you.
Name: The_Spectre
